Ash-Sheikh Muhammad Sani Yahaya Jingir, malamin addinin Musulunci na kungiyar Izala da ke Jos arewa ta tsakiyar Najeriya, wanda ya ce coronavirus ba gaskiya ba ce, yanzu ya ce tabbas cutar gaskiya ce.
Ash-Sheikh Muhammad Sani Yahaya Jingir, malamin addinin Musulunci na kungiyar Izala da ke Jos arewa ta tsakiyar Najeriya, wanda ya ce coronavirus ba gaskiya ba ce, yanzu ya ce tabbas cutar gaskiya ce.
